{
  "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.83,
      "size": 45216,
      "text": "欢迎来到数值分析的世界！数值分析是研究如何用计算机求解数学问题的学科。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.13,
      "size": 50112,
      "text": "在实际应用中，很多数学问题无法得到精确解，这时我们就需要使用数值方法来获得近似解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.79,
      "size": 44640,
      "text": "数值分析的核心问题包括：误差控制、算法稳定性、收敛速度和计算效率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "error-analysis",
      "line_id": "error-1",
      "filename": "error-analysis-error-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/error-analysis-error-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.65,
      "size": 58320,
      "text": "在数值计算中，误差是不可避免的。误差主要来源于三个方面：模型误差、截断误差和舍入误差。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "error-analysis",
      "line_id": "error-2",
      "filename": "error-analysis-error-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/error-analysis-error-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.44,
      "size": 55008,
      "text": "截断误差是由于用有限项代替无限项而产生的。例如，泰勒级数展开时只取前几项。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "error-analysis",
      "line_id": "error-3",
      "filename": "error-analysis-error-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/error-analysis-error-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.12,
      "size": 49968,
      "text": "舍入误差是由于计算机只能表示有限位数的数字而产生的。浮点数运算会累积舍入误差。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "error-analysis",
      "line_id": "error-4",
      "filename": "error-analysis-error-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/error-analysis-error-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "绝对误差是近似值与真实值的差，相对误差是绝对误差与真实值的比值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "ode-methods",
      "line_id": "ode-1",
      "filename": "ode-methods-ode-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/ode-methods-ode-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.58,
      "size": 57312,
      "text": "常微分方程在科学和工程中无处不在。欧拉法是最简单的数值解法，它用切线来近似曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "ode-methods",
      "line_id": "ode-2",
      "filename": "ode-methods-ode-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/ode-methods-ode-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.67,
      "size": 58752,
      "text": "欧拉法的公式是：y的下一个值等于当前值加上步长乘以导数。这是一阶方法，误差与步长成正比。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "ode-methods",
      "line_id": "ode-3",
      "filename": "ode-methods-ode-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/ode-methods-ode-3.mp3",
      "duration": 4.07,
      "size": 65088,
      "text": "龙格-库塔法是更高精度的方法。四阶龙格-库塔法使用四个斜率的加权平均，误差与步长的四次方成正比。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "ode-methods",
      "line_id": "ode-4",
      "filename": "ode-methods-ode-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/ode-methods-ode-4.mp3",
      "duration": 3.04,
      "size": 48672,
      "text": "RK4方法计算四个系数k1到k4，分别对应区间起点、中点和终点的斜率信息。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "stability",
      "line_id": "stability-1",
      "filename": "stability-stability-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/stability-stability-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.03,
      "size": 48528,
      "text": "数值稳定性是指算法对输入误差的敏感程度。一个稳定的算法不会放大输入误差。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "stability",
      "line_id": "stability-2",
      "filename": "stability-stability-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/stability-stability-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.79,
      "size": 60624,
      "text": "对于ODE求解，步长的选择至关重要。步长太大会导致不稳定，步长太小会增加计算量和舍入误差。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "stability",
      "line_id": "stability-3",
      "filename": "stability-stability-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/stability-stability-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.56,
      "size": 57024,
      "text": "刚性方程是指解的某些分量变化很快而另一些变化很慢的方程。求解刚性方程需要特殊的隐式方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "stability",
      "line_id": "stability-4",
      "filename": "stability-stability-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/stability-stability-4.mp3",
      "duration": 3.2,
      "size": 51264,
      "text": "条件数衡量问题对输入扰动的敏感度。条件数越大，问题越病态，数值求解越困难。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "root-finding",
      "line_id": "root-1",
      "filename": "root-finding-root-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/root-finding-root-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "size": 49536,
      "text": "求根问题是找到使函数值为零的点。二分法是最简单可靠的方法，它不断将区间对半分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "root-finding",
      "line_id": "root-2",
      "filename": "root-finding-root-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/root-finding-root-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.45,
      "size": 55152,
      "text": "二分法每次迭代将误差减半，这是线性收敛。虽然慢，但保证收敛，只要初始区间包含根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "root-finding",
      "line_id": "root-3",
      "filename": "root-finding-root-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/root-finding-root-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.46,
      "size": 55296,
      "text": "牛顿法使用函数的导数信息，收敛速度快得多。它是二次收敛的，每次迭代有效数字大约翻倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "root-finding",
      "line_id": "root-4",
      "filename": "root-finding-root-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/root-finding-root-4.mp3",
      "duration": 3.6,
      "size": 57600,
      "text": "牛顿法的缺点是需要计算导数，而且对初值敏感。如果初值选择不当，可能不收敛或收敛到错误的根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "convergence-1",
      "filename": "convergence-convergence-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/convergence-convergence-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "收敛性是指当步长或容差趋于零时，数值解是否趋于真实解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "convergence-2",
      "filename": "convergence-convergence-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/convergence-convergence-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.53,
      "size": 56448,
      "text": "收敛阶描述误差减小的速度。一阶方法误差与h成正比，二阶方法误差与h平方成正比。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "convergence-3",
      "filename": "convergence-convergence-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/convergence-convergence-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.39,
      "size": 54288,
      "text": "对于迭代方法，线性收敛意味着误差每次减少一个常数因子，二次收敛意味着误差每次平方减小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "convergence-4",
      "filename": "convergence-convergence-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/convergence-convergence-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "在实际应用中，我们需要在精度、稳定性和计算效率之间找到平衡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-1",
      "filename": "applications-applications-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/applications-applications-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "size": 49680,
      "text": "数值分析在科学计算中无处不在。天气预报使用数值方法求解大气动力学方程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-2",
      "filename": "applications-applications-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/applications-applications-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.19,
      "size": 51120,
      "text": "在工程设计中，有限元分析使用数值方法求解偏微分方程，模拟结构的应力和变形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-3",
      "filename": "applications-applications-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/applications-applications-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "size": 49536,
      "text": "机器学习中的优化算法，如梯度下降，本质上也是数值方法，用于最小化损失函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "applications",
      "line_id": "applications-4",
      "filename": "applications-applications-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/applications-applications-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "金融工程使用数值方法为期权定价，求解随机微分方程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-1",
      "filename": "summary-summary-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/summary-summary-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "数值分析提供了用计算机求解数学问题的系统方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-2",
      "filename": "summary-summary-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/summary-summary-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "理解误差来源和传播规律，是设计和使用数值算法的基础。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-3",
      "filename": "summary-summary-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/summary-summary-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "稳定性和收敛性是评价数值方法的两个关键指标。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-4",
      "filename": "summary-summary-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/summary-summary-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.44,
      "size": 39024,
      "text": "选择合适的数值方法需要考虑问题的特性、精度要求和计算资源。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "numerical-analysis",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "summary-5",
      "filename": "summary-summary-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/numerical-analysis/summary-summary-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "希望这个可视化工具能帮助你更好地理解数值分析的核心概念！"
    }
  ],
